{"tid":290853,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"2017香港紋身展討論","createTime":"2017-06-20T05:58:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-19T16:12:37.000Z","uid":83618,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8645b489e272d336f3ac349c95c47f1f258ec3fe","tid":290853,"uid":83618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T05:58:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">先小人:開post係為左交流討論紋身展，並非為左聽道地高地撚黎講耶穌，如果入黎係要屌紋身對錯，你可以出返去先，大家亦都無須爭論，文化差異姐</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hktattoocon.com/2017/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hktattoocon.com%2F2017%2F&d=P3Ct9nB%2Fhxif4vCYrtChYiwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=44d902d2\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hktattoocon.com/2017/</a><br />\n<br />\nDATE: 29 SEP TO 1 OCT 2017<br />\rTIME: 12NOON-10PM<br />\rVENUE: HALL A, 2/F, KAI TAK CRUISE TERMINAL, 33 SHING FUNG ROAD, KOWLOON, HONG KONG<br />\r\n<br />\n今年同上年一樣都係遊輪碼頭，<br />\n我搵到資料唔多，希望有巴絲打補充<br />\n<br />\n我分享下上年去經驗(今年未必相同)<br />\n<br />\n1.門票有3日通行同1日<br />\n<br />\n2.碼頭無ATM，但場內只收現金<br />\n<br />\n3.多數都無得DIY圖案，只可以就攤位師父提供既選擇<br />\n<br />\n4.有師父係會展覽後會繼續係酒店做生意<br />\n<br />\n5.可以即場紋身，但有機會個紋身師太多人選擇而即日做唔到，另外紋之前記得傾好價錢同埋紋身要求大細之類<br />\n<br />\n6.部分紋身師輪候情況比較亂，所以見到d非登記而係口頭就咁幫你排，最好小心d<br />\n<br />\n7.要多比較價錢同個風格岩唔岩自己。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果巴絲打有更多經驗可以分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有錯可指出<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後就係紋身前三思，後悔都幫你唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e781729693771ae445564f7f792064c517a25b0","tid":290853,"uid":611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T06:12:10.000Z","msg":"很想去 唔知會唔會平過平時紋"},{"pid":"c4464e59adcd56f93d6e6f64e2914cf863fe5486","tid":290853,"uid":83618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T06:36:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>很想去 唔知會唔會平過平時紋</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會，香港紋身係貴小小，熟人另計<br />\n我係場內問左右手前臂各紋一個拳頭size既英文字<br />\n<br />\n香港既答我2k-3k<br />\n台灣開2k<br />\n最後簡左個外國黎自南美洲既紋身師收我1k"},{"pid":"439778aeffa5fea8e705d651753eab8f7a5bdae5","tid":290853,"uid":12324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T07:28:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a5a492cf641f85434d7ec553d0d2ba49e39d4c24","tid":290853,"uid":83618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T08:41:56.000Z","msg":"喱到無人會去？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d88f0fd4414e5bc10ff41fec1878bf21dab9cc4c","tid":290853,"uid":58666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T08:49:26.000Z","msg":"有興趣 不過想去望下 欣賞下得唔得? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a82b1bdbe43592f34e0980c217cf886bb5b8ebc","tid":290853,"uid":83618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T09:41:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有興趣 不過想去望下 欣賞下得唔得? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你買門票入就得，正如你去其他展覽都可以剩睇無消費"},{"pid":"95afff480eda6c8dae5706d831d3c8f6fce32a5a","tid":290853,"uid":44641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T09:51:20.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上年有去開眼界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3dc480b8b04300a4a9ebf7c8447956f1c4f3f2a","tid":290853,"uid":83618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T09:58:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上年有去開眼界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我上年去係第一次紋身"},{"pid":"67bbc585c3d0aacfbb7ab0cb55a23a9bdfe6e1ec","tid":290853,"uid":44641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T10:01:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上年有去開眼界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我上年去係第一次紋身</blockquote><br />\n你係諗好哂搵邊個紋乜野 先入場搵嗰個紋身師紋 定係入到去行行下合眼緣就紋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"085b12b9934269c3d79c863d60ac12f94cde9127","tid":290853,"uid":83618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T10:06:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上年有去開眼界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我上年去係第一次紋身</blockquote><br />\n你係諗好哂搵邊個紋乜野 先入場搵嗰個紋身師紋 定係入到去行行下合眼緣就紋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我本身想紋字，所以入去會睇下邊d紋身師係專門紋字<br />\n諗定好d，不過你有時間買3日門票去行咁就可以到時入去先慢慢望"},{"pid":"72602edd4ba743bdaa15da1cdf04ce75981ec37a","tid":290853,"uid":38103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T10:54:13.000Z","msg":"去到叫師傅幫我補色會唔會好ON9"},{"pid":"1ba99c3cab9dd1084cefa2a9aeb94091d6943429","tid":290853,"uid":83618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T11:16:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去到叫師傅幫我補色會唔會好ON9</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n喱個我未試過，所以唔清楚"},{"pid":"9978f90fd0f8e885455321761867602c33276768","tid":290853,"uid":10313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T12:36:36.000Z","msg":"啫係淨係可以講自己想紋乜唔可以帶圖？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9aa8d6c4664cc5ff0e12a0ff62b142c07412b41","tid":290853,"uid":48266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T13:04:06.000Z","msg":"留名 好想紋多個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾時知有邊啲師父參展？"},{"pid":"ddb281782f5890eb56bf0da470531ca5ee0fbc13","tid":290853,"uid":937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T13:05:52.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb859d3f69f2ec207a3cd74d03bb2dca5c849214","tid":290853,"uid":85515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T13:10:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>很想去 唔知會唔會平過平時紋</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會，香港紋身係貴小小，熟人另計<br />\n我係場內問左右手前臂各紋一個拳頭size既英文字<br />\n<br />\n香港既答我2k-3k<br />\n台灣開2k<br />\n最後簡左個外國黎自南美洲既紋身師收我1k</blockquote><br />\n有時唔可以用價錢黎衡量"},{"pid":"9cd1b0c5e8ec1f0ec4e9ff74d5694b6cdadd5381","tid":290853,"uid":83618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T13:41:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>很想去 唔知會唔會平過平時紋</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會，香港紋身係貴小小，熟人另計<br />\n我係場內問左右手前臂各紋一個拳頭size既英文字<br />\n<br />\n香港既答我2k-3k<br />\n台灣開2k<br />\n最後簡左個外國黎自南美洲既紋身師收我1k</blockquote><br />\n有時唔可以用價錢黎衡量</blockquote><br />\n一分錢一分貨我當然明"},{"pid":"32b89a814e781f53389ccae2488354b189d7ad55","tid":290853,"uid":83618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T13:41:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名 好想紋多個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾時知有邊啲師父參展？</blockquote><br />\n留意住個網吧"},{"pid":"2325583e1ce2a458eaba1b385f9fc912dc3c0b37","tid":290853,"uid":83618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T13:42:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啫係淨係可以講自己想紋乜唔可以帶圖？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n帶都無用，現場我無睇到可以DIY"},{"pid":"71ccf6e8b591eef11ed789ee56599857161239a4","tid":290853,"uid":44323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T13:44:13.000Z","msg":"紋唔紋大笨象？"},{"pid":"e67b55814c75c1d18e571ba2184d31b124e0ff1c","tid":290853,"uid":33567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T13:51:41.000Z","msg":"可以影相？"},{"pid":"eeb4d2227a9aa2aaf8535c60959aba0d4ead77e2","tid":290853,"uid":105280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T13:51:45.000Z","msg":"今年想去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />上年miss咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5452d49c53fd09185f0e17b9be14ff7f801208c7","tid":290853,"uid":83618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T14:34:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可以影相？</blockquote><br />\n可以，不過如果係d普通人地紋好，咁你問句表示尊重"},{"pid":"ac06f28ca3eeb284a72ebf3d4b0984ef8cf44a24","tid":290853,"uid":83618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T14:36:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>紋唔紋大笨象？</blockquote><br />\n唔明，你有無圖討論下"}]}